metadata.title: Hydrographic Profiles of the Gulf of Alaska, Bering Sea, Chukchi Sea, and Southeast Coastal Fjords

creators.name: University of Alaska Fairbanks (UAF), School of Fisheries
Ocean Sciences (SFOS), Institute of Marine Science (IMS)

metadata.description:
Contains hydrographic profiles of the Gulf of Alaska, Bering Sea, Chukchi Sea, and Southeast Coastal Fjords.  Profiles include salinity, temperature, sigma-t, delta-o, depth and occasionally oxygen, nutrient, chlorophyll, and productivity
data.
